text: Luis Ernesto Hinojosa Compres (born 1 November 1986), is a professional boxer from the Dominican Republic. He has held the WBA Fedecaribe flyweight and the WBA Fedelatin bantamweight titles. ==Professional career== ===World title fight=== Hinojosa lost to Yonfrez Parejo for the World Boxing Association bantamweight interim world title. ===Other notable opponents=== Hinojosa had a no contest against world title challenger Jonathan Guzmán due to an accidental headbutt. He also has a loss to world title challenger Claudio Marrero.
